                            <comment id="13719784" author="keithbarrette" created="Thu, 25 Jul 2013 17:10:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Would love to see this resolved - not a blocker, but it generates a bunch of log noise.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13727911" author="hojberg" created="Fri, 2 Aug 2013 18:14:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yea this generates a lot of noise in our logs. Would love to see it fixed&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13728174" author="jensg" created="Fri, 2 Aug 2013 21:56:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=keithbarrette&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;keithbarrette&quot;&gt;keithbarrette&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=hojberg&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;hojberg&quot;&gt;hojberg&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the main problem is, that unfortunately we can&apos;t accept pull requests. Could either one of you reach out to the original developer and have him/assist him in providing a patch following the guidelines at &lt;a href=&quot;http://thrift.apache.org/docs/HowToContribute&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://thrift.apache.org/docs/HowToContribute&lt;/a&gt; ? &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13728195" author="keithbarrette" created="Fri, 2 Aug 2013 22:18:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Taken from &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/evernote/evernote-sdk-ruby/pull/12&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/evernote/evernote-sdk-ruby/pull/12&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13728197" author="keithbarrette" created="Fri, 2 Aug 2013 22:19:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jensg&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jensg&quot;&gt;jensg&lt;/a&gt; done!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13728491" author="jensg" created="Sat, 3 Aug 2013 08:34:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Maybe I should not have used the word &quot;assist&quot; here. What I meant was, that the &lt;ins&gt;&lt;b&gt;original autor&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; of the patch has to grant permission to the ASF, which is done by uploading it into JIRA. Otherwise we could just do a pull.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13729618" author="keithbarrette" created="Mon, 5 Aug 2013 16:20:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jensg&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jensg&quot;&gt;jensg&lt;/a&gt; I misunderstood your comment - I&apos;ve reached out to the original author, hopefully he&apos;ll respond.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks again.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
